NOTE ON DATA FILES:
The data files under `data/raw/`, `data/rdf/`, and `data/goldset/` are
derivatives of publicly available Korean government budget explanation
documents (예산설명서) published by the Ministry of Economy and Finance and
other central government agencies. They are included here under the original
government public-data terms; please cite the original sources when using
them. The MIT License above applies to source code only.

NOTE FOR DOUBLE-BLIND REVIEW:
During the review period, see LICENSE_REVIEW_ONLY.txt for the short notice.
The MIT License above applies to the camera-ready public release.
